story.title: Littlefield - Part 3
story.storyDescription: Sarah finds a dead body in the woods and uncovers a dark and deadly mystery.

messages.text: Nora, are you around??
Hold on.
Finishing up a tarot reading for some idiot who’s asking me if she’s pregnant.
BUY A TEST LADY!!!
Sarah is missing.
Sarah who??
Sarah Henning. She apparently never got home last night.
That neighbor you have a crush on who doesn’t really like you back?
Shut up. I’m really worried she was one of the people who got killed...
or if she’s with someone else
What do you mean, one of the people who got killed!?
Didn’t you hear!? There’s a town-wide curfew tonight...
because they found a bunch of bodies in the North Woods.
Nora??
Sorry…
What??
I’ve been having weird dreams and feeling this kind of dread all week.
Like something really bad was about to happen.
Can you pick up on whether or not Sarah was one of the people murdered?
HELLO?
I don’t actually feel there is a murderer out there
Well, clearly that’s fucking WAY off.
Listen, if you’re going to be insulting what I’m saying...
because it doesn’t fit what is convenient for you, then we can be done here.
No, I’m sorry. Please keep going.
Let me pull the cards first before I tune in anymore...
I got this:
She’s fucking dead…Oh my God….
The death card doesn’t mean literal death here. It means transitions or change.
Intuitively, I don’t feel like she’s dead. Something else is happening though.
Like what?
The tower shows something traumatic.
The eight of swords might indicate that she’s maybe trapped somewhere...
but that’s about to change (which is what death means)
Trapped!? Trapped where?
I don’t know…Give me a second to center myself.
Was there a barn anywhere near where you were last night?
I don’t think so. I don’t know. I’m not too familiar with the area
Who’s Dylan?
Fuck…
What?? Wait is that???
The fucking dangerous dealer guy I told you to stay away from!??
He called me before, she was supposed to drop money we owe him off.
She never got there and now he’s threatening to cut off my balls.
Jokes on him, since you don’t have any.
And WHY would you hook up the person you had a crush on with someone dangerous like that!?
She WANTED to start dealing.
College is going to be fucking expensive you know
Jesus, Jared, everything you touch turns to shit doesn’t it.
I need you to give me more details, Nora!
Is she alive, does she have the money? WHERE is she??
Maybe you can ask the radio people you talk about.
Listen, I’m NOT your psychic whore and this girl is NOT your girlfriend...
so I’m not contacting the radio people.
You have NO idea what happens with them and what they do to me.
Not to mention, they only come out when really epic shit is about to go down.
Listen, I’ve got money.
NO.
Nora, please. I’m in love with her. My life might be in jeopardy.
I need help
Then you’re going to have to just settle for the old fashion way.
Just give me a second to tap in again…
Thanks…
Oh god
What!?
There’s a barn, and a man…a few of them… they’re acting like animals
What does that mean!!? ARE THEY HURTING HER!!?
Nora??
NORA???
WHERE DID YOU GO???
I’m getting in the car, on my way over.
It’s Nora’s brother Elliot, what the fuck did you say to her??
Why??
Because it’s fucking happening again
What’s going on?? Is she okay??
If you call having a seizure okay, then yeah!!
How is that my fault???
DID YOU MENTION THEM!?
Who??
THE RADIO PEOPLE!? DID YOU GODDAMN MENTION THEM??
I mean we briefly touched on them, but she refused to use them
Listen, they use HER.
And she’s been able to avoid then for months, and now while talking to you...
she fucking dropped to the floor and is foaming at the mouth.
Are they saying anything??
That’s the first thing you ask!?!?
Please, if they do, it’s important
My sister isn’t your 5 o’clock news
PLEASE, they’d only speak through her if it’s important, right?
She said the words Saint Rhiannon. Sound familiar??
Saint Rhiannon? I don’t know…
Well you better start googling asshole!
Wait, is she saying anything else??
No, she just stopped. My Mother got an ice pack for her head.
She’s just laying here and needs to rest, which is code for YOU CAN FUCK OFF NOW
Can you put me on with her??
NO.
Please, I’m begging you…
All she said to tell you was “this is just the beginning.”
What does that mean!?!?!
She passed out.
Click below to see what happens next...
